{"id":94,"parent_id":80,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":94,"title":"Mosiah 14","subtitle":"","short_title":"Mosiah","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 14"],[".studySummary",["i","Isaiah speaks messianically—The Messiah’s humiliation and sufferings are set forth—He makes His soul an offering for sin and makes intercession for transgressors—Compare",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/53"},"Isaiah 53"],". About 148",["span.small","B.C."]]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.1","order":"05.19.014.9992"},["b","1"],"Yea, even doth not Isaiah say: Who hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"believed"],"our report, and to whom is the arm of the Lord revealed?"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.2","order":"05.19.014.9993"},["b","2"],"For he shall grow up before him as a tender plant, and as a root out of dry ground; he hath no form nor comeliness; and when we shall see him there is no beauty that we should desire him."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.3","order":"05.19.014.9994"},["b","3"],"He is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"despised"],"and rejected of men; a man of sorrows, and acquainted with grief; and we hid as it were our faces from him; he was despised, and we esteemed him not."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.4","order":"05.19.014.9995"},["b","4"],"Surely he has",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"borne"],"our",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"griefs"],", and carried our sorrows; yet we did esteem him stricken, smitten of God, and afflicted."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.5","order":"05.19.014.9996"},["b","5"],"But he was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"wounded"],"for our",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"transgressions"],", he was bruised for our iniquities; the chastisement of our peace was upon him; and with his stripes we are",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"healed"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.6","order":"05.19.014.9997"},["b","6"],"All we, like",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"sheep"],", have gone astray; we have turned every one to his own way; and the Lord hath laid on him the iniquities of us all."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.7","order":"05.19.014.9998"},["b","7"],"He was oppressed, and he was afflicted, yet he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"opened"],"not his mouth; he is brought as a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"lamb"],"to the slaughter, and as a sheep before her shearers is dumb so he opened not his mouth."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.8","order":"05.19.014.9999"},["b","8"],"He was taken from prison and from judgment; and who shall declare his generation? For he was cut off out of the land of the living; for the transgressions of my people was he stricken."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.9","order":"05.19.014.10000"},["b","9"],"And he made his grave with the wicked, and with the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"rich"],"in his death; because he had done no",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"evil"],", neither was any deceit in his mouth."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.10","order":"05.19.014.10001"},["b","10"],"Yet it pleased the Lord to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"bruise"],"him; he hath put him to grief; when thou shalt make his soul an offering for sin he shall see his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"seed"],", he shall prolong his days, and the pleasure of the Lord shall prosper in his hand."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.11","order":"05.19.014.10002"},["b","11"],"He shall see the travail of his soul, and shall be satisfied; by his knowledge shall my righteous servant justify many; for he shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"bear"],"their iniquities."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.12","order":"05.19.014.10003"},["b","12"],"Therefore will I divide him a portion with the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"great"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"he"],"shall divide the spoil with the strong; because he hath poured out his soul unto death; and he was numbered with the transgressors; and he bore the sins of many, and made",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"intercession"],"for the transgressors."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.1a","order":"05.19.014.10004"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/53.1.1-12"},"Isa. 53:1 (1–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.3a","order":"05.19.014.10006"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/22.6"},"Ps. 22:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/19.14"},"1 Ne. 19:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.4a","order":"05.19.014.10008"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/7.11"},"Alma 7:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.4b","order":"05.19.014.10010"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.17"},"Matt. 8:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.5a","order":"05.19.014.10012"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-crucifixion-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Crucifixion of"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.5b","order":"05.19.014.10014"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/15.9"},"Mosiah 15:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/11.40"},"Alma 11:40"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.5c","order":"05.19.014.10016"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/2.24.24-25"},"1 Pet. 2:24 (24–25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.6a","order":"05.19.014.10018"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/9.36"},"Matt. 9:36"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/12.5"},"2 Ne. 12:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/28.14"},"28:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.37"},"Alma 5:37"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.7a","order":"05.19.014.10020"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/53.7.7-8"},"Isa. 53:7 (7–8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/15.3.2-14"},"Mark 15:3 (2–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/19.9.9-10"},"John 19:9 (9–10)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/2.23.22-23"},"1 Pet. 2:23 (22–23)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/15.6"},"Mosiah 15:6"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-trials-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Trials of"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.7b","order":"05.19.014.10022"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.19"},"Jer. 11:19"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/passover"},"TG Passover"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.9a","order":"05.19.014.10024"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/27.57.57-60"},"Matt. 27:57 (57–60)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/15.46.27,43-46"},"Mark 15:46 (27, 43–46)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-death-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Death of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.9b","order":"05.19.014.10026"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/19.4"},"John 19:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.10a","order":"05.19.014.10028"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/3.15"},"Gen. 3:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/16.20"},"Rom. 16:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.10b","order":"05.19.014.10030"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/15.10.10-13"},"Mosiah 15:10 (10–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.11a","order":"05.19.014.10032"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/16.22.21-22"},"Lev. 16:22 (21–22)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/3.18"},"1 Pet. 3:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/19.16.16-19"},"D&C 19:16 (16–19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.12a","order":"05.19.014.10034"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/24.26"},"Luke 24:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.12b","order":"05.19.014.10036"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/15.12"},"Mosiah 15:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"12c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.12c","order":"05.19.014.10038"},["b","12c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/2.9"},"2 Ne. 2:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/15.8"},"Mosiah 15:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/7.28.27-28"},"Moro. 7:28 (27–28)"],"."]]}
